Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.57,Secondary,Sanji,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.62,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Estou aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:34.66,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,para você.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.55,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ele resistiu! Ótimo trabalho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.10,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,É por causa da reabilitação dele e porque a Nami está de casaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.10,Thoughts,Caribou,0,0,0,,{ def: madhouse instead of dangerous? }Este navio é perigoso! Eu tenho que me salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.34,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Algo está se aproximando por trás.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.20,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Esse é o navio de antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.75,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Coribu! Vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:00.68,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Você voltou para me salvar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.08,Main,Coribou,0,0,0,,Nós vamos te salvar, mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.65,Main,Pirates,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.08,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,O revestimento da bolha de sabão quebrou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.17,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}E aquele navio era ainda maior que o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:27.41,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.44,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Eles se parecem com águas-vivas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.75,Main,Caribou,0,0,0,,Cale a boca, Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.00,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Está vindo direto para nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.39,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,É muito grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fscx250}Engrenagem Terceiro-
